snippet.title: CHOP Release Trailer - Available September 13th 2019 - Switch and PC
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/755920/CHOP/
CHOP is a 2D party game with tons of gore and fast-paced action. Swords will fly, bodies will be chopped, friendships will break !
